Package com.github.oeuvres.alix.util

Class Edge

java.lang.Object
com.github.oeuvres.alix.util.Edge
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Edge>
public class Edge extends Object implements Comparable<Edge>
An edge between 2 int nodes with a score, optimized to be sorted by score in an Array, or to be a value in HashMap. Is not good as a key in an HashMap, because natural order is not good for sorting buckets in HashMap. Nodes are not mutable, but score is mutable, especially to be incremented as value in a Map.
